    "body": "I think the behavior of the `title` field is correct. Mac OS X exposes a native API for adding custom views to the bottom portion of the open/save dialogs, but I doubt Electron can support that in a generic way.\n\n@manovotny :  `command-shift-.` does work to show hidden files. \n"
